{"tid":2326492,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［廢佬輸唔起］千與千尋臨時更新票房紀錄成316.8億","createTime":"2020-12-15T11:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T14:19:18.000Z","uid":44598,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a5511ed2790878f4d2f418e8b2e68e61d9f6d846","tid":2326492,"uid":44598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:00:39.000Z","msg":"東寶今日亦公佈消息，由於《千與千尋》今年在疫情下再於當地戲院重映，並與吉卜力出品的《幽靈公主》、《地海傳說》及《風之谷》於6月至8月期間上映，《千與千尋》收約8.8億日圓（約6千600萬港元），令該片的票房數字改寫成316.8億日圓（約23.6億港元），被《鬼滅》破紀錄前罕有地更新總票房收入<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201215/N57ODA2YDFAQHGGY3HBUBZHPEQ/?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_content=share_link&amp;fbclid=IwAR215GopOGV9314pMG8uaUaKkrmVCcdfV9EA47xaFErv3YTv_w9mhDgn8TQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201215%2FN57ODA2YDFAQHGGY3HBUBZHPEQ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_content%3Dshare_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR215GopOGV9314pMG8uaUaKkrmVCcdfV9EA47xaFErv3YTv_w9mhDgn8TQ&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=8a099355\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201215%2FN57ODA2YDFAQHGGY3HBUBZHPEQ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_content%3Dshare_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR215GopOGV9314pMG8uaUaKkrmVCcdfV9EA47xaFErv3YTv_w9mhDgn8TQ&h=5918649e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201215/N57ODA2YDFAQHGGY3HBUBZHPEQ/?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_content=share_link&amp;fbclid=IwAR215GopOGV9314pMG8uaUaKkrmVCcdfV9EA47xaFErv3YTv_w9mhDgn8TQ</a>"},{"pid":"7cdf65db183e98f5921f9c4d392f65c08f7321ed","tid":2326492,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:11:54.000Z","msg":"鬼滅睇一次就夠"},{"pid":"32b9ee97858749bb1f3ff080b3